review.reviewBody: 4 Beignets were so good. Small portion though. Small portion too for Taster box (all for me).  Candies were average, nothing special. The pictures made both the beignets and the candy box look bigger than they actually are
This is the second time I've ordered the Date Night movie pack and they've given me the single. Come on guys, get it together.

I've ordered from here many times and everything has always been *chefs kiss*. Best ice cream sandwiches of all time. There was a mix-up with my most recent order and they very quickly resolved and were so kind over the phone. Would highly recommend!!!
really appreciate you guys taking my order close to closing and the extra chocolate. always a really top experience. I happily recommend you to my friends
Milkshakes were good but took 40 mins to make. way over the estimated
